Conditions
==========
Distribution of the Licensed Work, in Source or compiled form, is
subject to the following conditions:

  1. Attribution -- Any distributed copy must include a visible
     credit to the original project in both the documentation and
     in any user interface or "About" dialog. The credit must
     identify the copyright holder(s) named in the copyright
     notice of the Licensed Work.

  2. Copyright Notice -- All existing copyright notices must be
     retained in every copy, in both Source and compiled form. You
     may add Your own copyright notice to modifications You make.

  3. File-Level Copyleft -- If You modify a file of the Licensed
     Work, that modified file must be distributed under this License.
     Other files in the same distribution may remain under different
     terms. A "modified file" is one in which You add, delete, or
     change any lines of the file's content.

  4. License Copy -- When distributing Source form, You must include
     a copy of this License with the distribution.

  5. UI Notice in Modified Versions -- If You distribute a modified
     version of the Licensed Work as a standalone application or
     system, You must include a notice in the application's "About"
     or settings interface stating that the software is a modified
     version of the original Licensed Work.

  6. Sublicensing Restriction -- Any sublicense granted under this
     License must use this License with no additional restrictions.
     You may not impose any further restrictions on the rights
     granted herein.

